subject: Basketball
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Kia Vaughn had 13 points and 15 rebounds to help sixth-ranked Rutgers defeat No. 11 California Monday night, 56-51, in Piscataway, N.J.
